legacy.full_text: China has lodged a solemn representation to the US concerning two #US #arms sales ($440 mln) to #Taiwan, which Beijing considers "gross interference in internal affairs." A #PLA spokesperson says China will resolutely maintain stability across the Taiwan #Straits. @Frontlinestory https://t.co/DkMEJh7QiF

legacy.full_text: Antony #Blinken stressed the #US does not support “Taiwan #independence” during his visit to Beijing. China says the #separatists will not get any endorsement, and the Democratic Progressive Party authorities cannot deceive the people in #Taiwan. @Frontlinestory https://t.co/fTbPC2KtAZ
